			h2 How is it different to other frameworks?

			ul
				li Written in SASS, the best CSS pre-processor there is
				li Lightweight, includes only the most fundamenttl tools needed in web design (and you can even customise what's included)
				li Fully customisable - it's a boilerplace, not a framework




